name: GetFit
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: get fit
des:
This is a voice-controlled personal trainer which aims to build your body. Please say "Alexa, open Get Fit" to launch this skill. You will be prompted to say "start" to begin your daily exercise routine, and "ready" once you are ready for the next type of exercise.

The training routine is edited from this popular subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/bodyweightfitness/wiki/kb/recommended_routine, please visit the site for more information. 
Images are from Antranik, a professional trainer. Please visit http://antranik.org/ for clear instructions for the exercises (recommended).

This skill is still under development. Please feel free to give us feedback by writing a review!
